msgctxt "sn22.137:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.137:0.2"
msgid "14. Kukkuḷavagga "
msgstr "14. Burning Chaff "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.137:0.3"
msgid "137. Aniccasutta "
msgstr "137. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.178, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.2"
msgid "“Yaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ; tatra vo chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, you should give up desire for what is impermanent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.3"
msgid "Kiñca, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is impermanent? "

msgctxt "sn22.137:1.4"
msgid "Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ; tatra vo chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "Form is impermanent; you should give up desire for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.5"
msgid "Vedanā aniccā … pe … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.6"
msgid "saññā … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.7"
msgid "saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.8"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ; tatra vo chando pahātabbo. "
msgstr "Consciousness is impermanent; you should give up desire for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.9"
msgid "Yaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ; tatra vo chando pahātabbo”ti. "
msgstr "You should give up desire for what is impermanent.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.137:1.10"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
